Definition: dementia observed during the last stages of severe chronic alcoholism
Example: involves loss of memory for recent events although long term memory is intact
Synonyms: alcohol_amnestic_disorder, Korsakoff, s_psychosis, s_syndrome, Korsakov, polyneuritic_psychosis, dementia, observed, during, the, last, stages, of, severe, chronic, alcoholism, involves, loss, memory, for, recent, events, although, long, term, is, intact
Category: noun.state
